ğŸ”‘ 8ï¸âƒ£ Admin Login (Default Credentials)

If the database has the default admin from setup, use:

Email: danish@gmail.com
Password: admin


Otherwise, you can manually insert one in DB or via script:

from app import app, db
from models import User

with app.app_context():
    admin = User(first_name="Danish", last_name="Muzzafar",
                 email="danish@gmail.com", phone="12123456789",
                 address="Birmingham", password="admin", type="admin")
    db.session.add(admin)
    db.session.commit()

