ğŸ§° 10ï¸âƒ£ Common Issues & Fixes
Issue	Cause	Fix
ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'flask'	Flask not installed	pip install flask
sqlite3.OperationalError: no such table	DB not created	Run db.create_all() inside app context
Page not loading images	Wrong static path	Ensure /static/... paths are correct
Port already in use	Flask already running	Stop with Ctrl + C and rerun
